    "description": "Roll to move. Move to aim. Aim to win. <br>You're a square, and it's time to Square Off!<br><br>Up to 4 friends get to battle it out in this &quot;edgy&quot; arena party brawler with unique controls.<br><br><strong>A New Spin On 2D Platforming</strong><br>You move by rolling. You also aim by rolling. You can climb anything. Chaos reigns supreme with this control scheme.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/0ac6ac6c808ef3fa8e90b670743c51b1.poster.avif?t=1700720887\" width=612 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/0ac6ac6c808ef3fa8e90b670743c51b1.webm?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/0ac6ac6c808ef3fa8e90b670743c51b1.mp4?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>We Accept All Types Of Playstyles</strong><br>Want to play skillfully and maneuver like a master? That works.<br>Want to button mash and create mayhem wherever you roll? Yeah, that works too.<br><br><strong>Orient Yourself To Your Abilities</strong><br>Obliterate your friends with an array of unique abilities that attach themselves to one of your sides. Use these to fight off your friends! <br>If you survive long enough, you'll be able to pick up boosts that jetpack you across the map or shield you from harm.<br>If you keep surviving, acquire an ultimate ability to unleash complete devastation on your friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/ae91d3bcfa9b2a947e291cad5f37da69.poster.avif?t=1700720887\" width=612 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/ae91d3bcfa9b2a947e291cad5f37da69.webm?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/ae91d3bcfa9b2a947e291cad5f37da69.mp4?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Location Location Location</strong><br>A multitude of stages with unique mechanics add to the chaos by providing new possibilities for play, whether you're bouncing sky-high, knocking another player into lava, or throwing yourself through a teleporter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/6db04b7994560e1598084b49fea23fe8.poster.avif?t=1700720887\" width=552 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/6db04b7994560e1598084b49fea23fe8.webm?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/6db04b7994560e1598084b49fea23fe8.mp4?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Support For The Underdog</strong><br>Losing? Don't worry! With a variety of underdog powerups, no game will ever be truly lost as you unleash new powers that increase in power the further you are behind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/3f7a0a124fb27dcd49c749554a5ec13c.poster.avif?t=1700720887\" width=588 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/3f7a0a124fb27dcd49c749554a5ec13c.webm?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125340/extras/3f7a0a124fb27dcd49c749554a5ec13c.mp4?t=1700720887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Free Forever</strong><br>Play with your friends for free. This will never change regardless of how much new content goes into the game!",
